.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-QR" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-qr \- render a BOLT-11 invoice as a terminal QR code
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-qr
.I bolt11
.SH DESCRIPTION
Renders the BOLT-11 invoice as a UTF-8 QR code using
.B qrencode
if available.
Falls back to printing a
.B lightning:
URI JSON object when
.B qrencode
is not installed.
.PP
Output (qrencode present):
.nf
UTF-8 QR code on stdout
.fi
.PP
Output (fallback):
.nf
{"uri":"lightning:<bolt11>"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-qr (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-create (1)
